  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/7397de8830da7ec1147deb021253b31a.poster.avif?t=1684499956\" width=644 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/7397de8830da7ec1147deb021253b31a.webm?t=1684499956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/7397de8830da7ec1147deb021253b31a.mp4?t=1684499956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Starts on slow gear and explore. Enter timed stages portal to SHIFT GEARS! HURRY! Time is your Life.  Protect it to not lose precious seconds or XpP depending where you are.  Shoot enemies and blocks to unlock your path. Help the world inabitants by finding and collecting Time Bugs. Not fast or strong? Defeat enemies and collect xp orbs to LEVEL UP and upgrade! Lots of fun in a Short Game !Can cause rage attacks! Are you up to the task?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/3c0de006b270299089aaf2beef540dba.webp?t=1684499956\" width=644 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/910103fc43adbab9cbe16563a822bb97.poster.avif?t=1684499956\" width=644 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/910103fc43adbab9cbe16563a822bb97.webm?t=1684499956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463130/extras/910103fc43adbab9cbe16563a822bb97.mp4?t=1684499956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Short on time?. Here's a summary: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Slow overworld start<br></li><li> Fast paced levels<br></li><li> No life gauge. Time is your Life.<br></li><li> Level up and get stronger <br></li><li> Discover new abilities<br></li><li> Lots of bellybutton shooting<br></li><li> Amazing music<br></li><li> Find and catch the Time Bugs<br></li><li> Simple puzzles<br><br>-------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >XMAS UPDATE:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Enjoy Xmas with some snow and a new Skin. Wait for Christmas month <br>or JUST CHEAT and change your month to December to unlock it<strong></strong></li></ul></li></ul>",
